# Ainfera Cursor Rules

## Vocabulary (Ontology v1.0)

Entity classes (PascalCase): Tenant, Agent, AgentCard, Inference, Provider,
Model, Wallet, Ledger, LedgerEntry, AuditEvent, AuditChain, Settlement,
Skill, Receipt.

Retired (AIN-243 — do not reintroduce): TrustScore, Lens, Voter, Council.
Model trust is expressed as Routing `q_empirical`. See PURGE_LOG.md at the
repo group root for the full retirement list.

API paths (kebab-case): /v1/agents/:id · /v1/audit/:agent_id
JSON fields (snake_case): agent_id · created_at

## Banned terms
- "Exchange" -> "Infrastructure"
- "Platform" alone -> specific Layer name
- "User" (end-customer) -> "Agent" or "Tenant"
- "Spark/Hermes/Letta/Vox/Mythos" as Ainfera agent -> Manwe/Varda/Namo/Yavanna/Aule
- "hermes-agent" lowercase IS allowed (NousResearch framework)

## Style
- TypeScript: strict
- Python: mypy --strict, ruff, async by default
- Test before commit

